<sect>gugus
<p>
There are 4 ways to lock the screen:
<enum>
  <item>Click on the <url url="widget:/kpanel/lockButton" name="lockButton"> in the panel.
  <item>Click on a empty space on your <url url="term:/root_window" name = "root window"> and press the right mouse button.
        A popup-menu will appear. Now click on 'Lock screen'.
  <item>Just <url url="cmd:/klock" name="do it"> right now.
  <item><em>Experts:</em> Enter the command <tt>klock</tt> in a shell.You can get a prompt
        pressing <tt>Alt-F2</tt>
</enum>


